Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(622,544)}Well then, here's to our beloved Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(586,550)}...passing the W.D.C...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,552)}...right into the Tournament Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(606,546)}To summarize, he won the Semi-Finals and advanced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(613,554)}Congratulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he made it through the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Kotori... Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, are you {\i1}still{\i0} angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being left behind by Yuma on the Canyon Field...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I was sorry! I was so engrossed in the Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engrossed by butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck. Don't fuss.\N You suck. Don't fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiddies, the snacks are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starved!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must express your gratitude before you begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must pay your respects to the Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be sure to show your gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Yuma... there's bound to be a bunch of formidable opponents left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark, and Kaito, and Tron.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who it is! Bring 'em on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat it to 'em, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness... You barely won as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle it, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that we must not rush in\N unprepared against those remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron's Number is aided by the power of his Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito has his incredibly powerful Neo Galaxy Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was with that Chaos Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does he {\i0}have{\i1} a Chaos Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely gonna win the Duel Carnival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! As long as I got this deck a' mine with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And who exactly is Dr. Faker...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone! Gone! Gone! My deck's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my deck~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh... I seriously can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(518,514)}"Number 60: The Overture Towards the Final Battle:\N The New Foe Dr. Faker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually lost your important deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.\N It's already lost, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is it really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! There's a GPS feature attached to our deck cases
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that operates together with our D-Pads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s deck case is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here in Heartland!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(648,522)}Excuse me! Is there anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(667,528)}Please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,514)}It'll only take a second, so please do this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please open it!\N Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it! Open up already! Open up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they won't open it no matter what.\N Then we just gotta climb over and pass through!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obviously not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just think of it as the 30 step jumping blocks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is impossible to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh... You really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trucks entering over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the place where the trash collected by the O-Bots from the trash bins are returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a light bulb! It's the hidden side of this joint!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! We're gonna hide inside these trash bins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they go to return the trash the O-Bots take from the trash bins,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can sneak inside Heartland!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like it could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I'm preying for your success!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! That rascal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get this done with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He really got inside there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, it can't be helped.\N Help me out, Tetsuo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't really expect me to go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm worried about Yuma going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cat a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one more trash bin!\N I won't let Kotori take it from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I don't really want to go inside a trash bin {\i1}that{\i0} badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's really sly of you to try to go together with Yuma, cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't really think you'd be of any use, Kotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*Clank~*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, in that case, Cat-{\i1}chan{\i0} can go in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then! We'll decide this with rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how humans show affection for one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it simply their fighting spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to go in the trash bi-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you guys hurry it up already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right...\N - Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning! Cleaning! Cleaning! Cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash rejected. Trash rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why? Hang on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trash enough for this! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, everything went as I said it would, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is proceeding well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, all the Numbers will belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to make them pay for rendering III, IV, and V as sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity, but it was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected no less from my sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}IV... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please save Tron, my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryoga,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you'll definitely able to save my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the one who incriminated me and injured my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're responsible for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let you get away with it at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting, Ryoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Tron?! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you belong to {\i1}me{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably believe that you overcame your darkness in that Duel before,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was all as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IV worked diligently for this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll spread it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it into a darkness that far exceeds what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! Treating a lady like trash...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we were able to get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! We're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're falling! Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is this all trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's there such a huge garbage disposal underneath Heartland?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that vision just now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something happening here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:11:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto is above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto... Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an elevator over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he really is above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Intruder detected. Intruder detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Intruders will be eliminated through a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What'll we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wants to Duel, we're just gonna have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something just appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of cards just appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all Xyz Monster Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Scrap Recycler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the cards here are Xyz Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kotori, jump on the 3 panel in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I Xyz Summon with the two Level Threes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Wind-up Zenmaines!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Xyz Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Wind-up Zenmaines!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Recycler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Scrap Searcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, leave this to us and go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to meet Haruto-{\i1}kun{\i0}, don't you, Yuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this way, useless robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're your opponents here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori, press two Level Ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two ones... One... One... Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use three Level Ones to conduct an Xyz Summon! Come forth, Mira the Giant Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Attack Searcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Scrap Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori, press Level Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Shining Elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you guys! Tetsuo! Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I reached it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many does it have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is Haruto's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Haruto still hasn't regained consciousness from that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win the Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely beat that Tron down, and return as the champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hold back against even your brother, Kaito, when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't let Tron and the others take you that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma. Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed that you guys would come here eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto! Haruto, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother is already pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have the power to save my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I cannot get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto's consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto’s true consciousness was sealed deep inside his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are able to release his true consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe Haruto can recover from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how should we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not sure either. But maybe it has something to do with Kaito collecting Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I start collecting Numbers, Haruto may never get cured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Kaito collects them…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who’s battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus you should make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I lose, you'll disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I Dueled alongside you, I have learned a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started to think that I was glad I partnered with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow the path you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of path it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to say something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should shout and cry more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say, “Help me get back my memory! I don’t want to disappear like this!”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would help me harden my heart for the upcoming battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, why...? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're Kaito and Haruto's dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Kazuma Tsukumo's son, and the Original Number.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... knows about Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can see me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you collecting the Numbers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the Numbers my memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I made a deal with the Varian World.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varian World...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Another different world that coexists with the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I destroy the Astral World,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can obtain the strongest power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become the ruler of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! For that reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you forced Kaito to hunt the Numbers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you know how much Haruto and Kaito are suffering because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the both of them your own children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are just some minor sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to obtain the strongest power, sacrifices are unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, Haruto, and you, Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as your father, Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People always need to strive to survive while giving up something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Original.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking forward to tomorrow’s matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, treating people like trash again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heart Burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The World Carnival finally reaches its Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who will be the strongest Duelist that wins the honor as the first-generation W.D.C. Champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will now announce the match-ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron VS Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma VS Ryoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, I'm definitely gonna win the championship...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll resolve everything with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The W.D.C. Semi-Finals finally began!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My opponent is Shark, and I'll give you everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:23:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey! Shark!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Duel Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shark seems kinda strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the power of his Number...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll win! I will win this and awaken Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Vanishing Bond!\N Yuma VS Shark: The fated Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say? I made your sister… !?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faker's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.47,0:24:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, they're all men!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanna have an all-men family!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.79,0:24:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observation #20: "Akari is a woman".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.83,0:24:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just realized that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.73,0:24:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared.
